p.k: Short, Comedy, Romance France (2016). Hrají: Thomas Grascoeur, Ophélie Marsaud, Xavier Bonadonna. Režie: Thomas Grascoeur.
p.d: When 30-year-old Faustine comes back home to prepare herself before meeting her date she finds herself face to face with a stranger who has made himself at home in her apartment. What if apps became real people and actually lived in our homes ?
